strings: <voice_0x01000D9D><se_low>King of tricks: ... nine o'clock! What's going on here
<voice_0x01000D9E><se_low>King of tricks: We've heard of an accident in Peckham!
<voice_0x01000D9F><se_low>King of tricks: Dormigus's terrifying footprints can now be found!
<voice_0x01000DA0><se_low>King of tricks: Not bad though. How can you go to the beach with him? I must admit I'm a little confused.
<voice_0x01000DA2><se_low>King of tricks: do you know him Show me your card!
<voice_0x01000DA3><se_low>King of tricks: Let's check it out now. this is my opinion
<voice_0x01000DA4><se_low>King of tricks: and now... i'm here
<voice_0x01000DA5><se_low>King of tricks: He is getting better
<voice_0x01000DA6><se_low>King of tricks: We're just south of the castle! I didn't even know this house was close by.
<voice_0x01000DA7><se_low>King of tricks: Well...then I'll have to go back to the palace and see if I can find any information about this ship in the library. Maybe you also have some tips!
<voice_0x01000DA8><se_low>King of tricks: No time to waste. I'm back to work! in the palace
